
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
      <h4>Hello <%= "#{@application.firstname} #{@application.lastname}" %></h4>
    <p>
      This is a confirmation that you are enrolled for the Michigan
      Math & Science Scholars High School Program for the Summer <%= @camp_config.camp_year %> camp.
    </p>
    <p>
      Continue to check your email for any further updates.
    </p>
    <p>
      Retain the login id: <span class="text-semibold"><%= @user_detail.email %>
      </span> and password that you created during the application process. You
      will need it to refer back to the application web site to review the
      events associated with your application.
    </p>
    <p>
      <%= link_to 'MMSS - Michigan Math and Science Scholars', @url %>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
